<p>
  <span class="nym">Alleaume</span>
  <span class="gen">m.</span>
  
  <span class="etym"><span class="lang">Old High German</span> <i>adal</i> 'noble' + <span class="lang">Old High German, Old Saxon</span> <i>helm</i> 'helmet'.
  </span>
  
</p>
  
<div class="usg">
  <p>The name of a 10th C French saint.</p>
</div>
  
  


